data.description: Mid Century Modern gem nestled in the established neighborhood of Lake Harbor Shores. Free from homeowners association constraints, this rare find has potential as an excellent rental investment or charming primary residence. Following a $50k (+/-) renovation in 2024, including new HVAC system, upgraded kitchen, luxury vinyl plank flooring, and fresh paint throughout, this 3-bed, 2-bath property's open floor plan seamlessly blends comfort, style, and functionality. The home promises a move-in-ready experience. Practicality meets aesthetics with a 2-car garage and an unfinished basement, ready for conversion into a teen or in-law suite, with plumbing already in place for a bathroom and laundry. Perfectly located near Lake Lanier, enjoy tranquility. Just a 5-minute drive to parks like Little Hall, Long Hollow, and Keith Bridge; this location caters to outdoor enthusiasts. Likewise, retail therapy awaits only 15 minutes away at the North Georgia Outlets. Affordability, lifestyle; the complete package.
